@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_qnxmvq(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = ((wp.exp(tmp + 0.30) + v2) - wp.abs(wp.cos(v1 + 0.93)))
    tmp = v2
    tmp = 0.62
    tmp = wp.cos((0.32 - (v0 + 0.28 - v0 + 0.74)))
    v0 = wp.sin((wp.cos(tmp + 0.28) / wp.exp(v2 + 0.46)))
    data[tid] = v0
